OL,4,Cbuilding Britain's next battlefield
OL,5,Cvehicle
OL,7,F"Please don't go rogue with your
OL,8,Fcameras", we're told by a senior
OL,9,Fmanager at the General Dynamics
OL,10,Ffactory in Merthyr Tydfil.
OL,12,FDuring a briefing with media from all
OL,13,Fover the UK, there is good reason for
OL,14,Fthis polite request, as this facility
OL,15,Fin the shadow of the south Wales hills
OL,16,Fis building one of the most advanced
OL,17,Ffighting vehicles ever designed.
