OL,7,FThe Ajax "family of vehicles", refers
OL,8,Fto six variants of a tracked and
OL,9,Farmoured fighting vehicle built
OL,10,Fprimarily for the British Army and now
OL,11,Fbeing marketed to NATO countries to
OL,12,Fbuy for themselves.
OL,14,FAjax, Ares, Athena, Atlas, Apollo,
OL,15,FArgus. Each vehicle has a particular
OL,16,Frole on the battlefield ranging from
OL,17,Frepair and maintenance to delivering
OL,18,Fspecialist troops where they're most
OL,19,Fneeded. None of them are tanks,
OL,20,Ftechnically speaking at least.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/11
