OL,7,FIn total, the Merthyr factory and its
OL,8,Fengineers will deliver 589 of these
OL,9,Fvehicles. Along with other
OL,10,Fjournalists, I was given a rare
OL,11,Fglimpse into the working factory where
OL,12,F250 people build these impressive
OL,13,Fmachines part-by-part. We see turrets
OL,14,Fin various stages of build and huge
OL,15,Fengines waiting to be added to the
OL,16,Fvehicle carcasses.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/11
