OL,7,FOne apprentice said: "It's very
OL,8,Fsurprising when you first come in
OL,9,Fhere, there's just armoured vehicles
OL,10,Feverywhere. You obviously don't see
OL,11,Fthat every day. It doesn't get boring
OL,12,Fseeing it."
OL,14,FAnother added: "It's not a usual
OL,15,Fthing, especially as a girl in STEM.
OL,16,FEvery time I ever speak about General
OL,17,FDynamics, everyone is impressed."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/11
