OL,7,FBut the army has had to be patient,
OL,8,Fbecause this #5.5 billion programme
OL,9,Fhas been beset with issues and delays.
OL,10,FIt's finally been granted Initial
OL,11,FOperating Capability, a status that
OL,12,Fmeans the first batch of 50 vehicles
OL,13,Fand their trained crews are ready to
OL,14,Fbe deployed to a warzone. When the
OL,15,Fproject was first announced 16 years
OL,16,Fago, that was expected to be delivered
OL,17,Fby 2017.
