OL,7,FMost of the issues were discovered
OL,8,Fearly in testing, when "excessive
OL,9,Fvibration and noise" was so severe
OL,10,Fthat several soldiers had to be
OL,11,Ftreated for hearing loss. The UK
OL,12,FGovernment's Defence Readiness
OL,13,FMinister, Luke Pollard MP came to
OL,14,FMerthyr this week on a mission to
OL,15,Freassure - particularly the potential
OL,16,Fbuyers around Europe - that the Ajax
OL,17,Fgroup of vehicles were safe for
OL,18,Fsoldiers to operate and well-worth the
OL,19,Finvestment.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/11
