OL,7,FThe UK Government's Defence Readiness
OL,8,FMinister, Luke Pollard MP, said: "The
OL,9,Fobjective of this government is not
OL,10,Fonly to deliver the nearly 600
OL,11,Fvehicles that we're buying for the
OL,12,FBritish Army, but to work with our
OL,13,Finternational allies to sell this
OL,14,Fplatform for our allies to use as
OL,15,Fwell."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/11
