OL,7,FHe added: "It is a safe vehicle for
OL,8,Four people to use, but importantly, it
OL,9,Fis also lethal against any adversary.
OL,10,FIt is now a successful project; we've
OL,11,Flearned the lessons from what went
OL,12,Fwrong under the last government. I now
OL,13,Fsee a bright future for AJAX and,
OL,14,Fhopefully, an opportunity to bring
OL,15,Fmore export orders to South Wales,
OL,16,Fcreating more good jobs."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/11
