OL,7,FThe Army expects that the building and
OL,8,Ftraining programme for Ajax will be
OL,9,Fcomplete by 2030. So far, General
OL,10,FDynamics in Merthyr have delivered
OL,11,Fover 150 vehicles, with more emerging
OL,12,Ffrom the factory every month.
OL,14,FEven at a price of between #8 and #15
OL,15,Fmillion for just one vehicle, 8 NATO
OL,16,Fmember countries are said to be
OL,17,Finterested in buying Ajax. The workers
OL,18,Fin this impressive factory will hope
OL,19,Fthose decisions will bring long term
OL,20,Fsecurity to their jobs.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/11
